div.p:
“Protect me from those who consume vitality and fetuses;  who drink
                        blood; who consume fat, flesh, grease, marrow, and newborns; who steal life;
                        who consume vomit, feces, and urine; who drink sewage and devour leftovers;
                        who drink saliva and consume snot, mucus, filth, oblations, flower garlands,
                        fragrances, and incense; who capture people’s minds; and who consume
                        flowers, fruits, grains, and burnt offerings!
